spec_data.Name: python3-treq
spec_data.Description:
treq is an HTTP library inspired by requests but written on top of
Twisted’s Agents.
It provides a simple, higher level API for making HTTP requests
when using Twisted.

spec_data.Summary: A requests-like API built on top of twisted.web's Agent
